READING THIS FILE
-----------------

For the licenses of the Rust crates statically linked into the binary, see the
appended "RUST DEPENDENCY LICENSES" section (generated from the lockfile at
release time via `cargo about`; see docs/release/LICENSE_INVENTORY.md §A).

