recorded in section 7:

  * latexml-oxide's own source is CC0-1.0 — https://github.com/dginev/latexml-oxide
  * libmarpa 8.6.2 sources are vendored verbatim in the `libmarpa-asf-sys` crate
    (libmarpa-8.6.2.tar.gz), published to crates.io from https://github.com/dginev/marpa
